<body>
  <Header />
  <main>
    <div class="textbook-header">
      <h1>📖 Solar Irradiance and PV Power Forecasting</h1>
      <div class="meta">
        Dazhi Yang & Jan Kleissl · CRC Press, 2024 · 682页 · 12章<br/>
